upload_enable missing or off	Reject the POST with 403 Forbidden or 501 Not Implemented
upload_enable on, but upload_path missing	Return 500 Internal Server Error or use a default path
upload_enable on and upload_path valid	Proceed with the file upload

Method is POST	Maybe
Content-Type: multipart/form-data	✅ Very likely
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="..." inside body	✅ Definitely

